86,-0.03863829,0.21328452,0.01098268,-0.00582679,-0.00218759,-0.05540062,0.02618141,-0.03148293,-0.02675992,-0.01519219,-0.0052144,0.08051913,-0.01809737,0.01844984,0.01248809,-0.03134935,0.05585101,0.03050925,0.02530795,-0.10557603,0.03848417,-0.03126947,0.02217197,0.10131846,0.02582593,-0.0480838,-0.0241065,-0.03394835,0.10206681,-0.01704274,-0.04075188,0.0051276,0.00850992,-0.02481016,0.06600445,-0.01303279,-0.0249259,-0.01969209,-0.01550309,0.05584788,0.05847926,-0.0228279,0.04364023,0.03121323],"last_embed":{"tokens":316,"hash":"1b2ljo2"}}},"last_read":{"hash":"1b2ljo2","at":1780740308154},"class_name":"SmartSource","last_import":{"mtime":1780740240005,"size":9850,"at":1780740308068,"hash":"1b2ljo2"},"blocks":{"#":[1,93]},"outlinks":[{"title":"图片","target":"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/sz_mmbiz_jpg/iarPlJhMzOLmyj73pO5NkA6BaDBdVJgQ7kgNdwfzxNNgPSfbIvSG6bIfiaHH4zKNRElxAGWBBt1kIgLr7S3tLoicZ6gGTQLeU7uePnx4xah5mM/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&from=appmsg&wxfrom=13&tp=wxpic#imgIndex=1","line":5,"embedded":true},{"title":"AI自我进化的速度已经远远超出了人类的预期。为了避免人类彻底失去对技术的控制，Anthropic正式向全球发出呼吁，在建立起多国核查、监督机制的前提下，共同放缓或暂停AI研究","target":"https://www.anthropic.com/institute/recursive-self-improvement","line":11},{"title":"WMO发布了一份新的厄尔尼诺/拉尼娜通报，其显示2026年6月至8月期间发生厄尔尼诺事件的可能性为80%。该事件至少持续到11月的概率接近或超过90%","target":"https://wmo.int/news/media-centre/wmo-prepare-el-nino","line":31},{"title":"对于6月至8月期间，全球几乎所有地区气温都将以普遍高于正常水平为主。这增加了某些地区热应激和复合灾害的风险，并在降雨减少的地区加速干旱条件的发展","target":"https://news.sciencenet.cn/htmlnews/2026/6/565912.shtm","line":35},{"title":"CAR-T疗法或能帮助改造这些患者的免疫系统，已经帮助两名男性和一名女性成功接受了挽救生命的肾移植手术，且恢复良好","target":"https://www.nature.com/articles/d41586-026-01761-9","line":47},{"title":"2024年，在接受单次注射，以及额外药物促进T细胞增殖5个月后，该女性的抗体水平下降到可以接受肾移植","target":"https://www.nejm.org/doi/10.1056/NEJMc2517277","line":51},{"title":"首批两名受试者均为男性，他们也接受了CAR-T疗法，主要靶向CD19的T细胞，以及携带BCMA（另一种抗体生成细胞的蛋白标志物）的T细胞","target":"https://www.nejm.org/doi/10.1056/NEJMoa2513428","line":55},{"title":"图片","target":"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/iarPlJhMzOLnXbaY3yW22vX8bAZrHeVhfl8cSiar6D6NicOaCUBEJJlhgen3sQ2638ib2gcibKI8ybQEtYiaqtR3ibA5oLW5Xt6ftsSbr05BDt3psU/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&from=appmsg&tp=wxpic&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1#imgIndex=2","line":67,"embedded":true},{"title":"《科学》","target":"https://www.science.org/doi/10.1126/science.ady1618","line":73},{"title":"随后极度严苛的对照实验也证实了这种蜜蜂灵活的问题解决能力：它们会在行动前花时间审视和“思考”，极像人类在脑海中演练方案的过程","target":"https://www.science.org/content/article/bees-just-did-something-no-other-insect-has-been-shown-do","line":77},{"title":"Biophysical Journal","target":"https://www.cell.com/biophysj/fulltext/S0006-3495\\(26\\","line":89}],"task_lines":[],"tasks":{},"codeblock_ranges":[]},"smart_blocks:五篇文章.md#": {"path":null,"last_embed":{"hash":"1b2ljo2","at":1780740308154},"embeddings":{"TaylorAI/bge-micro-v2":{"vec":[-0.13328278,-0.0185749,-0.00954484,-0.04212262,-0.00173187,-0.01127217,-0.0291818,0.02575377,0.02336568,-0.02941898,0.03301801,-0.06444585,0.04157931,0.03514688,-0.01143565,0.03993354,0.02239984,-0.01416489,-0.07073993,-0.01248751,0.05753545,-0.01871704,0.00904565,-0.07147497,0.00279691,0.03365213,0.00635373,-0.02512074,0.00219351,-0.14016847,-0.03327534,0.03681806,0.0516313,-0.00190431,0.03225789,-0.00889515,-0.04473068,0.02317585,-0.05154727,0.01301216,0.01691516,0.05072261,0.07365027,-0.01319909,0.04959184,-0.00108266,0.00765424,-0.04498835,-0.04212366,-0.02281255,-0.03465231,0.0075259,0.02925607,0.04805274,0.03662369,0.03214854,0.06465156,0.04371095,0.04169959,0.05224971,0.05252191,0.06918858,-0.204431,0.05894061,0.0371446,-0.04136163,-0.02352492,-0.03040184,0.02770502,0.06516959,-0.04048251,0.01547093,0.01147992,0.02978114,0.0264796,-0.00160437,0.04024042,-0.07381921,-0.00584529,-0.02361886,-0.02790212,0.03043881,-0.07103018,-0.02846861,-0.02788475,0.03159726,0.04353604,-0.06786731,-0.00246155,-0.01184616,-0.00065739,-0.05060104,-0.03242534,0.03510679,-0.000969,-0.04706373,-0.0070151,0.01648388,-0.05335598,0.08585766,-0.04706617,0.01441244,0.04030001,-0.05109662,-0.02013945,-0.02852012,-0.01386701